    dc:description "Fig. 3. Left lateral view of anal fin pterygiophores in M. pataxo (a) and M. parahybae (b). Abbreviations: ar, anal-fin rays; dr, distal radial; lp, laminar process; pr, proximal radials; rr, rudimentary ray; up, uncinate process. Scale bar, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5418284/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5418286>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Cranium ofMicroglanis pataxo,MNRJ 28398, paratype. Dorsal view.Abbreviations: ao, antorbital; ep, epioccipital; fr, frontal; ffr, frontal fontanell; fso, parieto-supraoccipital fontanel; io, anterior, middle and posterior infraorbitals; le, lateral ethmoid; mx, maxilla; na, nasal; pa, autopalatine; pm, premaxilla; pt, pterotic; sc, posttemporosupracleitrum; so, parietosupraoccipital; sp, sphenotic. Scale bar, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5418286/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

