<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5418298>
    dc:description "Fig. 9. a. Drainage map of eastern Brazil between rio São Francisco and rio Paraíba do Sul illustrating the distribution of the Microglanis species in the area. Dotted line indicates the study area. Symbols may represent more than one locality. b. Detail of collecting localities of Microglanis pataxo in the study area, between the rio Mucuri and rio Jequitinhonha." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5418298/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

